<emphasis box="[1066,1226,1059,1083]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="29">S. h. hollandi</emphasis>
, but the hindwing disc is much darker (blackish-brown). Adult wingspan is on average 
<quantity box="[1038,1126,1091,1115]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="30" pageNumber="29" unit="mm" value="60.0">60 mm</quantity>
. Forms of this subspecies may have been referred to as 
<taxonomicName authority="dos Passos and Grey" authorityName="dos Passos and Grey" box="[548,1101,1123,1147]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Speyeria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="atlantis" subSpecies="lurana">
<emphasis box="[548,846,1123,1147]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="29">Speyeria atlantis lurana</emphasis>
dos Passos and Grey
</taxonomicName>
in the past.
</paragraph>
